            <string language="en">AP Environmental Science Virtual Labs</string>

            <string language="x-mt-fr">Laboratoires Virtuels de la Science

            <string language="x-mt-pt">Laboratórios Virtuais Da Ciência Ambiental do

          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">Welcome to the UCCP Advanced Placement (AP) Environmental Science Virtual Labs. These simulation and standard labs have been extracted from the AP Environmental Science course and put together in its own section.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Science and Technology</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Willkommen zu den UCCP hochentwickelte Plazierung 
(AP) Klimawissenschaft virtuellen Labors. Dieses sind Simulation
und Standardlabors vom AP Klimawissenschaft Kurs extrahiert worden und
zusammenfügten in sein eigenes Kapitel.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Bienvenue aux laboratoires virtuels de la Science 
environnementale avançée du placement d'UCCP (AP). Ces la 
simulation et les laboratoires standard ont été extraits à partir 
du cours environnemental de la Science de AP et ont remonté dans sa 
propre section.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Boa vinda da ciência ambiental avançada da 
colocação de UCCP aos laboratórios virtuais (AP). Este a 
simulação e os laboratórios padrão foram extraídos do curso 
ambiental da ciência do AP e unidos em sua própria seção.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Benvenuto ai laboratori virtuali di scienza 
ambientale avanzata di disposizione di UCCP (AP). Questo la 
simulazione ed i laboratori standard sono stati estratti dal corso 
ambientale di scienza di AP ed hanno unito nella relativa propria 
sezione.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Υποδοχή στα προηγμένα UCCP εικονικά εργαστήρια 
επιστήμης τοποθέτησης (AP) περιβαλλοντικά. Αυτά τα 
προσομοίωση και πρότυπα εργαστήρια έχουν εξαχθεί από την 
περιβαλλοντική σειρά μαθημάτων επιστήμης AP και έχουν τεθεί 
μαζί στο τμήμα της.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Recepción a los laboratorios virtuales de la 
ciencia ambiental avanzada de la colocación de UCCP (AP). Este 
la simulación y los laboratorios estándares se han extraído del 
curso ambiental de la ciencia del AP y juntaron en su propia sección.</string>
          </description>
